zbar (Bar code reader)

ZBar Bar Code Reader is an open source software suite for reading bar
codes from various sources,  such as video streams,  image files, and
raw intensity sensors.  It supports EAN-13/UPC-A, UPC-E, EAN-8,  Code
128,  Code 39,  Interleaved 2 of 5,  and QR Code.  Included  with the
library are basic applications for decoding  captured bar code images
and using a video device (e.g. webcam) as a bar code scanner.

http://sourceforge.net/projects/zbar